    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered here is a well-maintained 2018 Porsche Macan finished in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been driven with care and presents beautifully. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the lower rear bumper\u2014imperfections typical of road use but barely noticeable from a distance. The interior features premium Black leather that remains supple and clean; the bolsters show only minimal softening, and the cabin is free of any smoke or pet odors. All onboard electronics, including the navigation, premium sound system, and heated seats, are in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. It comes with a complete service log, including a fresh oil change and a recent multi-point inspection. The brakes are responsive, and the tires have approximately 60% of their tread remaining. This is a reliable, performance-oriented SUV that has been kept in solid condition, ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
